              <p>The Conflict Resolution Module will teach you about the different types of issues people face, cool down strategies, and conflict resolution strategies.  In addition, this module will allow you an opportunity to identify conflicts and solutions.</p>
              <h4>Introduction</h4>
              <p>Conflict is a normal part of the human experience.  It occurs when two or more people want different things.  Conflict can occur between friends, family members, and even strangers.</p>
              <h4>Negative Results of Conflict</h4>
              <p>Sometimes when people disagree on something or want different things, the following negative consequences occur: </p>
              <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-responsive">
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <ul>
                          <li>Intimidation (verbal or physical)</li>
                          <li>Harassment (verbal or physical)</li>
